Create Segments with Fewer Clicks

Create segments faster using the provided default values for the data space, segment on, schedule, segment type fields, and aggregation operator. If thereâ€™s only one possible value, Data Cloud sets it for you. For fields with multiple values, the most common choice is the default.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This functionality is available starting in July 2024.
